                'rubric_levels' => [
                    '1' => 'Dismisses the alarm as another false alarm based on Chief Engineer\'s assessment without investigating the new evidence (steward report, warm door, haze). Or alternatively, fails to differentiate at all and treats it identically to the previous false alarms.',
